g.text: Authors
contributions
YLL and FMY conceived and planned the project, provided the samples and
purified nucleic acids for sequencing. JX and GZ performed the whole
genomic amplification of genomic DNA, undertook the sequencing,
assembly and annotation of genomic. RR and AA planned and performed
additional bioinformatic analyses. WCL and YLL did literature searching.
YLL and WCL drafted and edited the manuscript, tables, figures and
supplementary information. AA curated the browsable genome. All authors
read and approved the final manuscript.
Acknowledgements
This research project was supported by University of Malaya High Impact
Research (HIR) Grant UM-MOHE (UM.C/HIR/MOHE/MED/16) from the Ministry
of Higher Education, Malaysia. We would like to express our gratitude to Prof.
Dr. Robin Gasser for his contributions of advises and ideas.
